Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for a place to stay, I was looking for happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to lose it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desperately grasping for every moment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I can do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.49,0:00:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dance in the light, but you're too far away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anger and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you see there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just gazing at those feathers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.57,0:01:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You muttered that you wanted to be human
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words and the kindness are different
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness is not the same for everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the very beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to open up and reach out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with all the mistakes, this is the cry of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a breath and shed a tear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:02:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be human
